{
  "stem": "25639.10",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother received six letters from me, all at the same time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although I've written many more, a number of other letters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they probably arrived later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at that time, the post office was in a chaotic situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was after the war, everybody was looking for everybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And many people were missing for a long time, for years actually.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the post office was in a chaos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Governments changed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Borders changed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so it's understandable that it would take so long to straighten out this sort of system.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But one day I received this precious letter from my mother that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she and Annuska were liberated from Auschwitz on January 27th, 1945, by the Soviet Army.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they sent them back home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It would take them-- they didn't get home till March.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It would take them so long to get home on foot, by train, by truck, by farmer's wagon, whatever they found on the road, whatever vehicles.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They would hitchhike, and they would be picked up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they would be taken to the next town and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When they came home, they learned that my brother, Michael, my oldest brother, was already home and found no one home and left.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Indeed, he was also liberated by the Soviet Army from slave labor camps and death marches.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was also sent home, but he left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But in those days, survivors in my part of the woods went to train stations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And people were going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were looking for each other, for somebody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so they hung around, wherever there was train movement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's where he was.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
